      "value": "<p>Your companion is an alchemical ooze that extends pseudopods to move around.</p><p><strong>Size</strong> Medium or Large</p><p><strong>Melee</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> pseudopod (agile), <strong>Damage</strong> 1d6 bludgeoning</p><p><strong>Str</strong> +3, <strong>Dex</strong> +2, <strong>Con</strong> +3, <strong>Int</strong> â€“4, <strong>Wis</strong> +0, <strong>Cha</strong> +0</p><p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 6</p><p><strong>Skill</strong> Athletics</p><p><strong>Motion Sense</strong> Your oozeform chair can sense nearby creatures through vibration in the air. This is an imprecise sense with a range of 30 feet.</p><p><strong>Speed</strong> 20 feet</p><p><strong>Special</strong> mount</p><p><strong>Support Benefit</strong> A pseudopod extends out from your chair, retrieving an unattended object within 15 feet. If you don't have a hand free to receive the object, the chair drops it in your space.</p><p><strong>Advanced Maneuver</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-animal-companions.AC-Advanced-Maneuvers.Item.gzefJocgdWbXWWPi]{Extend Pseudopod}</p>"
